    "We set up and ran the model with the Ollama framework.",
    "During tests with the larger 34b and 70b Instruct models, the models frequently refused to produce SPARQL queries \"due to safety concerns.\"",
    "These experiments were run on a gpu_1x_a100_sxm4 machine, rented from the Llambda GPU Cloud.",
    "The full GPU specs are provided in Table 1.",
    "The total costs for renting the GPU was 51.45 USD."
